      "path": "/books/al-kafi:7:4:39:16",
      "text": [
        " إِنَّ الْغُرَّةَ تَزِيدُ وَ تَنْقُصُ وَ لَكِنْ قِيمَتُهَا أَرْبَعُونَ دِينَاراً ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Mahboub, from Is’haq Bin Ammar, ",
          "Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> has said: ‘The commencement of the foetus increases and (sometimes) it is deficient, but its value is forty Dinars’."
        ]
